{
  "stem": "10283.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I have to tell you also that when they bought these tickets on the Saint Louis, the line, the Hamburg America line, asked already for return tickets.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they had already an inkling that this ship will not be able to land.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or in any event, they wanted the money for-- for both-- for both ways.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they were so glad that they got even a passage, that they got this cabin on the ship, that they took what they could, and they paid-- paid that and never even thought much about that.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was a terrible scene that I will never forget when we left our grandparents, you know, especially my mother's mother screamed like terrible.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we went to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we got on the boat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was only 16 at this time, so I didn't take it so terribly you know, hard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was with my parents, and it was an ocean voyage, my first ocean voyage.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother had made a long party dress for me, and I was learning how to dance no the ship.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- you know, before that, in Germany, I belonged to the [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Vakloid, ?] I belonged to the Zionist youth group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't indulge in any of this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had-- I remember, we had a letter in school from a girl that had immigrated to Brazil already.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she said, you wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The children here, they wear lipstick, and they wear nail polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, for us, that was so unusual and so-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we didn't believe in all that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We wore heavy shoes, and blouses, and skirts, and we were Zionist pioneers, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I wanted to go to Israel too on the Youth Aliyah.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
